Interface InstrumentedWorkerTask

  • All Superinterfaces:
    gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity, ProfilerDataSource
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface InstrumentedWorkerTask
extends ProfilerDataSource, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity
    Instrumentation information for a run of a distributed worker instance.
